&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Very exciting new post for a Community Nurse Specialist in the Bideford/Fremington Team of Community Nurses.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will work clinically to offer expert direction and day to day leadership to a team of community nurses. Hold a patient caseload and delegate work to the community nursing team. Provide assessment and nursing care, advice and information to patients and carers within the home environment or alternative care setting within the community.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a permanent post full time post working 37.5 hours per week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;** As this post is in a shortage occupation code it qualifies for the Trust’s Recommend a Friend Scheme, please find further information on the attached link**&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing date: 06/11/2020&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
